Last sentence is please see the permissions guide.  "permissions guide" is not a variable in the property value. In Turkish it'not possible to translate as the sentence structure is not english-like.

h5. Steps to reproduce:
# Create a page in Confluence.
# Export the page to Word document.
# Upload the document into the page.
# Display the file using {viewdoc} or {viewfile} macros.
# The out are as follows:
{code}
"Error rendering macro 'viewdoc': java.lang.RuntimeException: com.aspose.words.FileCorruptedException: The document appears to be corrupted and cannot be loaded."{code}
and{code}
"viewfile: java.lang.RuntimeException: com.aspose.words.FileCorruptedException: The document appears to be corrupted and cannot be loaded."{code}

It seems that the exported Word document is actually a html file with .doc extension.

